<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FreeRTOS Learning Roadmap</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Exo+2:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --green: #00ff88;
    --green-dim: #00cc6a;
    --green-glow: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.15);
    --amber: #ffb700;
    --red: #ff4466;
    --blue: #00aaff;
    --bg: #050a08;
    --bg2: #0a1210;
    --bg3: #0f1c18;
    --border: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.2);
    --text: #c8ffe8;
    --text-dim: #5a8f75;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Exo 2', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Grid bg */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(0,255,136,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,255,136,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* Scanline */
  body::after {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      0deg,
      transparent,
      transparent 2px,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 2px,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 4px
    );
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 24px 80px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    animation: fadeDown 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .header-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: var(--green);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    background: var(--green-glow);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--green);
    text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,255,136,0.5), 0 0 60px rgba(0,255,136,0.2);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  /* PHASES */
  .phases {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Vertical line */
  .phases::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
      transparent,
      var(--green-dim) 5%,
      var(--green-dim) 95%,
      transparent
    );
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .phase {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease forwards;
  }

  .phase:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .phase:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }
  .phase:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .phase:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.65s; }
  .phase:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .phase:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.95s; }

  .phase-left {
    flex: 1;
    padding-right: 40px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .phase-right {
    flex: 1;
    padding-left: 40px;
  }

  .phase:nth-child(even) .phase-left { order: 3; text-align: left; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0; }
  .phase:nth-child(even) .phase-center { order: 2; }
  .phase:nth-child(even) .phase-right { order: 1; text-align: right; padding-right: 40px; padding-left: 0; }

  .phase-center {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    min-width: 60px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .phase-dot {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--green);
    background: var(--bg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,255,136,0.3);
    z-index: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .phase-line {
    flex: 1;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin-top: 4px;
    min-height: 40px;
  }

  /* CARD */
  .card {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 24px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px; left: -1px;
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--green);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--green);
  }

  .card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1px; right: -1px;
    width: 20px; height: 20px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);
    border-right: 2px solid var(--green);
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--green-glow), inset 0 0 30px var(--green-glow);
  }

  .phase-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .phase:nth-child(even) .phase-header {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .phase-title {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .phase-tag {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    border: 1px solid;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .tag-beginner { color: var(--green); border-color: var(--green); background: rgba(0,255,136,0.08); }
  .tag-intermediate { color: var(--amber); border-color: var(--amber); background: rgba(255,183,0,0.08); }
  .tag-advanced { color: var(--red); border-color: var(--red); background: rgba(255,68,102,0.08); }
  .tag-expert { color: var(--blue); border-color: var(--blue); background: rgba(0,170,255,0.08); }

  .duration {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .duration span {
    color: var(--amber);
  }

  .topics {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .topic-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .topic-item::before {
    content: '▸';
    color: var(--green);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 10px;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }

  .topic-sub {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 3px;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .tools-section {
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding-top: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .tools-label {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .tools-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .tool-chip {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* MILESTONE bar */
  .milestone {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 10px 0 30px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .milestone-inner {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--bg3);
    border: 1px solid var(--amber);
    padding: 8px 20px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--amber);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,183,0,0.1);
  }

  /* FINAL */
  .final-section {
    margin-top: 60px;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease 1.1s both;
  }

  .final-title {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .resources-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .resource-card {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 20px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .resource-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 2px;
  }

  .res-book::before { background: var(--green); }
  .res-hw::before { background: var(--amber); }
  .res-project::before { background: var(--blue); }
  .res-community::before { background: var(--red); }

  .resource-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .resource-title {
    font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--green);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .resource-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
  }

  .resource-list li {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    padding-left: 12px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .resource-list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--border);
  }

  @keyframes fadeDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .phases::before { left: 24px; }
    .phase { flex-direction: column; }
    .phase-left, .phase-right,
    .phase:nth-child(even) .phase-left,
    .phase:nth-child(even) .phase-right {
      order: unset;
      text-align: left;
      padding: 0 0 0 60px;
    }
    .phase-center { position: absolute; left: 0; }
    .phase { position: relative; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .phase-dot { margin-top: 16px; width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 12px; }
    .phase-line { display: none; }
    .phase:nth-child(even) .phase-header { flex-direction: row; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-badge">// LEARNING ROADMAP v2.0</div>
    <h1>FREE<br>RTOS</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Real-Time Operating System for Embedded & IoT Systems</p>
  </div>

  <div class="phases">

    <!-- PHASE 1 -->
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-left">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-title">NỀN TẢNG C & EMBEDDED</div>
            <span class="phase-tag tag-beginner">BEGINNER</span>
          </div>
          <div class="duration">⏱ Thời gian: <span>4–6 tuần</span></div>
          <div class="topics">
            <div class="topic-item">
              Lập trình C nâng cao: con trỏ, struct, union, bit manipulation
              <div class="topic-sub">→ Hiểu rõ memory layout, stack vs heap</div>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Kiến trúc vi điều khiển: ARM Cortex-M, registers, pipeline
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              GPIO, UART, SPI, I2C — giao tiếp phần cứng cơ bản
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Interrupt & Exception handling — NVIC, priority
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Linker scripts, startup code, memory map
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tools-section">
            <div class="tools-label">// TOOLS</div>
            <div class="tools-list">
              <span class="tool-chip">GCC ARM</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">STM32CubeIDE</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">Keil MDK</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">OpenOCD</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-center">
        <div class="phase-dot">01</div>
        <div class="phase-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-right"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- PHASE 2 -->
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-left"></div>
      <div class="phase-center">
        <div class="phase-dot">02</div>
        <div class="phase-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-right">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-title">KHÁI NIỆM RTOS CƠ BẢN</div>
            <span class="phase-tag tag-beginner">BEGINNER</span>
          </div>
          <div class="duration">⏱ Thời gian: <span>3–4 tuần</span></div>
          <div class="topics">
            <div class="topic-item">
              RTOS là gì? So sánh Bare-metal vs RTOS
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Task / Thread: tạo, xóa, trạng thái (Ready, Running, Blocked, Suspended)
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Scheduler: preemptive vs cooperative scheduling
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Task priority & tick interrupt — configTICK_RATE_HZ
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Stack size calculation & stack overflow detection
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tools-section">
            <div class="tools-label">// BOARD GỢI Ý</div>
            <div class="tools-list">
              <span class="tool-chip">STM32F103</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">ESP32</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">Arduino Due</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="milestone">
      <div class="milestone-inner">✦ MILESTONE 1 — Hello FreeRTOS: Chạy được 2 tasks nhấp nháy LED song song</div>
    </div>

    <!-- PHASE 3 -->
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-left">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-title">ĐỒNG BỘ HÓA & GIAO TIẾP</div>
            <span class="phase-tag tag-intermediate">INTERMEDIATE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="duration">⏱ Thời gian: <span>5–6 tuần</span></div>
          <div class="topics">
            <div class="topic-item">
              Queue — truyền dữ liệu giữa các tasks & ISR
              <div class="topic-sub">→ xQueueCreate, xQueueSend, xQueueReceive</div>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Semaphore: Binary & Counting — đồng bộ sự kiện
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Mutex & Recursive Mutex — bảo vệ tài nguyên dùng chung
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Event Groups — chờ nhiều sự kiện đồng thời
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Task Notifications — nhẹ hơn semaphore, không cần kernel object
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Priority Inversion & Priority Inheritance
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-center">
        <div class="phase-dot">03</div>
        <div class="phase-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-right"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- PHASE 4 -->
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-left"></div>
      <div class="phase-center">
        <div class="phase-dot">04</div>
        <div class="phase-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-right">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-title">MEMORY & TIMER</div>
            <span class="phase-tag tag-intermediate">INTERMEDIATE</span>
          </div>
          <div class="duration">⏱ Thời gian: <span>3–4 tuần</span></div>
          <div class="topics">
            <div class="topic-item">
              Heap management: heap_1 → heap_5, pvPortMalloc/vPortFree
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Memory pools & static allocation — tránh heap fragmentation
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Software Timers: one-shot vs auto-reload
              <div class="topic-sub">→ xTimerCreate, xTimerStart, Timer Callback</div>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Tickless Idle Mode — tiết kiệm năng lượng cho IoT
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Stream Buffer & Message Buffer (FreeRTOS v10+)
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tools-section">
            <div class="tools-label">// DEBUG TOOLS</div>
            <div class="tools-list">
              <span class="tool-chip">FreeRTOS+Trace</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">Percepio Tracealyzer</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">SEGGER SystemView</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="milestone">
      <div class="milestone-inner">✦ MILESTONE 2 — Xây dựng hệ thống cảm biến + display với Queue và Timer</div>
    </div>

    <!-- PHASE 5 -->
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-left">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-title">IoT & CONNECTIVITY</div>
            <span class="phase-tag tag-advanced">ADVANCED</span>
          </div>
          <div class="duration">⏱ Thời gian: <span>6–8 tuần</span></div>
          <div class="topics">
            <div class="topic-item">
              FreeRTOS + TCP/IP Stack (FreeRTOS+TCP hoặc LwIP)
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              MQTT trên FreeRTOS — AWS IoT, MQTT Broker
              <div class="topic-sub">→ coreMQTT library, TLS/SSL</div>
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              ESP-IDF + FreeRTOS: Wi-Fi, BLE tasks management
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              AWS FreeRTOS / Amazon FreeRTOS — cloud connectivity
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              OTA (Over-The-Air) firmware update với FreeRTOS
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Low-power design: eTaskConfirmSleepModeStatus, portSUPPRESS_TICKS_AND_SLEEP
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tools-section">
            <div class="tools-label">// PLATFORMS</div>
            <div class="tools-list">
              <span class="tool-chip">ESP32</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">STM32WL</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">nRF52840</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">AWS IoT</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-center">
        <div class="phase-dot">05</div>
        <div class="phase-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-right"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- PHASE 6 -->
    <div class="phase">
      <div class="phase-left"></div>
      <div class="phase-center">
        <div class="phase-dot">06</div>
        <div class="phase-line"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-right">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-title">KERNEL INTERNALS & OPTIMIZATION</div>
            <span class="phase-tag tag-expert">EXPERT</span>
          </div>
          <div class="duration">⏱ Thời gian: <span>8–12 tuần</span></div>
          <div class="topics">
            <div class="topic-item">
              Đọc và hiểu FreeRTOS source code — tasks.c, queue.c, timers.c
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Context switching cơ chế — PendSV, SVC handlers trên ARM
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Port layer tự viết cho MCU mới
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Worst-case execution time (WCET) analysis & deadline scheduling
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Porting FreeRTOS lên RISC-V, MIPS, Xtensa
            </div>
            <div class="topic-item">
              Functional Safety: IEC 61508 / ISO 26262 với RTOS
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tools-section">
            <div class="tools-label">// REFERENCES</div>
            <div class="tools-list">
              <span class="tool-chip">FreeRTOS Source</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">ARM TRM</span>
              <span class="tool-chip">MISRA-C</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="milestone">
      <div class="milestone-inner">✦ MILESTONE FINAL — Deploy IoT device lên cloud với FreeRTOS + MQTT + OTA</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- RESOURCES -->
  <div class="final-section">
    <div class="final-title">// TÀI NGUYÊN HỌC TẬP</div>
    <div class="resources-grid">
      <div class="resource-card res-book">
        <div class="resource-icon">📖</div>
        <div class="resource-title">SÁCH & DOCS</div>
        <ul class="resource-list">
          <li>FreeRTOS.org Official Docs</li>
          <li>Mastering the FreeRTOS Kernel (miễn phí)</li>
          <li>Using the FreeRTOS Real Time Kernel</li>
          <li>The Definitive Guide to ARM Cortex-M</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="resource-card res-hw">
        <div class="resource-icon">🔌</div>
